OL,3,CNo extra homes to be used for asylum
OL,4,Cseekers following city's housing crisis
OL,6,FNo additional homes in Portsmouth will
OL,7,Fbe used for people seeking asylum,
OL,8,Faccording to the city council.
OL,10,FLast year, the authority declared a
OL,11,Fhousing crisis after demand for
OL,12,Ftemporary accommodation rose by 54%
OL,13,Fand costs for it increased by 84%.
OL,15,FThe Government runs a national scheme
OL,16,Fto distribute people seeking asylum
OL,17,Facross the country.
