OL,3,CNo extra homes to be used for asylum
OL,4,Cseekers following city's housing crisis
OL,6,FAsylum accommodation in Portsmouth is
OL,7,Fcommissioned by the Government and
OL,8,Fmanaged by a company called
OL,9,FClearsprings Ready Homes in the south
OL,10,Fof England on its behalf.
OL,12,FPortsmouth City Council said it was
OL,13,F"hosting more than its share of people
OL,14,Fseeking asylum" and lobbied the
OL,15,FGovernment to look elsewhere.
