OL,3,CNo extra homes to be used for asylum
OL,4,Cseekers following city's housing crisis
OL,6,FSteve Pitt, Leader of Portsmouth City
OL,7,FCouncil, said: "We've consistently
OL,8,Fsaid the Government should look at
OL,9,Fother areas before placing more people
OL,10,Fin Portsmouth and they now seem to be
OL,11,Flistening.
OL,13,F"We understand asylum is a national
OL,14,Fissue and we will support those the
OL,15,FGovernment places in our city but we
OL,16,Fhave a housing crisis and already
OL,17,Ffulfil our share.
